15 Section 301. For purposes of Section 301 et seq. of this title:
16 1. The term “cigarette” is defined to mean and include all
17 rolled tobacco or any substitute therefor, wrapped in paper or any
18 substitute therefor and weighing not to exceed three (3) pounds per
19 thousand cigarettes. The term cigarette shall include products that
20 are intended to be heated or burned;
